Add Liquidity Tip: When you add liquidity, you are given pool NFT representing your position. These NFT automatically earn fees proportional to your share of the pool, and can be redeemed at any time.
Remove Liquidity Tip: Removing pool tokens converts your position back into underlying NFT at the current rate, proportional to your share of the pool. Accrued fees are included in the amounts you receive.
Toggle Expert Mode Tip: Allow high price impact trades and skip the confirm screen. Use at your own risk.
Toggle Expert Mode Text1: Expert mode turns off the confirm transaction prompt and allows high slippage trades that often result in bad rates and lost funds.
Toggle Expert Mode Text2: ONLY USE THIS MODE IF YOU KNOW WHAT YOU ARE DOING.
